OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly mist, patchy fog or low
OL,6,Fcloud will disperse leaving bright
OL,7,Fconditions as high cloud increases.
OL,8,FChance of an afternoon shower. Highest
OL,9,Ftemperatures across western areas,
OL,10,Fcooler near coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy start to the evening
OL,13,Fwith some coastal showers. The cloud
OL,14,Fwill break inland but linger around
OL,15,Fthe coasts. Ground frost patches
OL,16,Fpossible in rural areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
